derivedClaims.name: Other Claims
derivedClaims.description: Have a fresh day with Mentos Pure Fresh chewing gum! This 80 piece bottle of Mentos Pure Fresh, Spearmint flavored chewing gum comes in category’s first recyclable paperboard format! In response to consumer requests for less plastic packaging, Perfetti Van Melle is bringing to market its universally loved Mentos Pure Fresh gum in 90% paperboard bottles. Each bottle contains sugar-free, Spearmint flavored gum that gives you a blast of fresh flavor that lasts chew after chew. Sugar-free for a guilt-free flavor sensation!

derivedClaims.name: Features & Benefits
derivedClaims.description:
• CONTENT: 80 piece bottle of Mentos Pure Fresh sugar-free chewing gum
  • FLAVOR: Long lasting Spearmint
  • SUSTAINABILITY: Bottle made from 90% paperboard and recyclable with clear recycle symbol & instructions on pack​
  • FREE OF: Sugar
  • XYLITOL: Number one ingredient is xylitol, which may help reduce the risk of tooth decay
  • BOTTLE: Great for the car, desk, and pantry​

derivedClaims.name: Storage Instructions
derivedClaims.description: STORE IN A COOL DRY PLACE
